            "stanza_text": "IL nous sied de remercier\nSur tous les tons de tous les modes\nBallades, sonnets, stances, odes,\nLe sage, le juste Mercier."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Car quelle guerre à l’Épicier",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Qui trouve ses us incommodes,",
